[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>dice</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: dice
<hw>dice</hw> <pr>(d⟦imac⟧s)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Diced</conjf> <pr>(d⟦imac⟧st)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Dicing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Cooking)</fld> <def>To cut into small cubes; <as>as, to slice and
<ex>dice</ex> carrots</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To ornament with squares, diamonds, or
